From {{L.}} '''[[transoceanicus]]''', from '''[[trans]]''', ''across'', plus '''[[oceanicus]]''', ''oceanic'', from {{Gr.}} '''[[οκεανικος]]''' ('''[[okeanikos]]'''), from '''[[okeanos]]''', ''ocean'', plus adjective suffix '''[[-ικος]]''' ('''[[-ikos]]'''))

===Adjective===
'''transoceanic'''
# [[beyond]], [[crossing]], or on the other side of an [[ocean]]

